-- SAP’s Cloud Computing May Not Be Profitable by 2013, Welt Says
-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 2012-04-26T06:34:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-26/sap-s-cloud-computing-may-not-be-profitable-by-2013-welt-says.html
SAP AG (SAP) ’s cloud-computing business
won’t be profitable this year,  Welt  said, citing an interview
with Chief Financial Officer Werner Brandt.  It’s too early to say whether the business, software sold
as an on-demand service, will be profitable by 2013, Werner
said, according to the German newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
